{"tid":111973,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Imagine Dragons啲歌啲詞其實唔錯","createTime":"2017-02-07T19:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T12:11:20.000Z","uid":27741,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47c84ad68baf82cef212eb017efda599a9243dc9","tid":111973,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T19:04:56.000Z","msg":"可能有共嗚？每個人聽都會諗起啲故事<br />\n一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Monster</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">If I told you what I was<br />\nWould you turn your back on me?<br />\n<br />\nI'm only a man with a candle to guide me<br />\nI'm taking a stand to escape what's inside me<br />\nI've turned into a monster</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">自己有好灰嘅一面 驚會嚇親身邊人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Demons</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em><span style=\"color: teal;\">No matter what we breed<br />\nWe still are made of greed</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">依個唔洗講</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Shots</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>From the second that I was born<br />\nIt seems I had a loaded gun<br />\nAnd then I shot, shot, shot a hole through everything I loved</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">好多野唔識珍惜 包括已逝去之人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">I bet my life</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">I know I took the path<br />\nThat you would never want for me<br />\nI know I let you down, didn't I?<br />\n<br />\n... I gave you hell through all the years...<br />\n<br />\nI've told a million lies <br />\nbut now I tell a single truth<br />\nThere's you in everything I do<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">想同爸爸講</span><br />\n<br />\n好 灰完再起步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Here we are<br />\nDon't turn away now</span><br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"0a96fdefe105f9ddb7337fdabc0299db0d599e0f","tid":111973,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b22666277f39c018300c731384c5ff6affb2846","tid":111973,"uid":27741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:50:55.000Z","msg":"Round 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Dream</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>And I'm short of the others' dreams<br />\nOf being gold and on top<br />\n<br />\nIt's not what you painted in my head<br />\nThere's so much there instead of all the colours that I saw<br />\n<br />\nWe all are living in a dream<br />\nBut like ain't what it seems<br />\nOh everything's a mess<br />\n<br />\nBut I wanna dream</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">人根本只需平凡過活 但係現實好似唔准 現實係你平凡就冇出息 <br />\nBut I wanna dream<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Trouble</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>Oh quiet down<br />\nI've had enough<br />\n<br />\nI need redemption<br />\nI'm just a man<br />\n<br />\nI want no trouble</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">生活真係好多煩惱</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Thief</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>If only you, you could see<br />\nThe darkest place that you could be<br />\n...there's so much more than you could know <br />\n<br />\nThe more I see, the more I know<br />\n<ins>That everyone just wants a show<br />\nNo we don't want to see the truth</ins><br />\n<br />\nWhen the stars look down on me<br />\nWhat do they see?</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">每個人都有黑暗面 或者一啲灰暗嘅情感 <br />\n有啲人 包括我 好想有人明白<br />\n但係你自己以外嘅人只會想睇你表面 <br />\nno one fucking cares about your mind<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Battle cry</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>Just one more time before I go<br />\nI'll let you know<br />\nThat all this time I've been afraid<br />\nWouldn't let it show</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">平時可能有啲人處事好冷靜<br />\n但對正經大事好恐懼<br />\n但係形象問題 又怕俾人知心事<br />\n所以要收埋<br />\n可能直到有一日會忍唔到... </span><br />\n<br />\n灰完又光返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">The time will come when you'll have to rise<br />\nAbove the best, improve yourself<br />\nYour spirit never dies<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"8dad11155a83deca16463648b286a52275238dcb","tid":111973,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:00:57.000Z","msg":"Demons<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a370518cc8625f1d6838dfe584485b6adced0a65","tid":111973,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:03:19.000Z","msg":"I'm starting to cave I'm losing my flame<br />\nI wanted your truth but I wanted the pain to disappear<br />\ndream maker, life taker<br />\nopen up my mind"},{"pid":"794fadd337329c9a2c1190456f412ed96145ee24","tid":111973,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:03:50.000Z","msg":"Hi Brett<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f28a479779e4f6e4824d7f6bbe7d3925e2ab0e","tid":111973,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I'm starting to cave I'm losing my flame<br />\nI wanted your truth but I wanted the pain to disappear<br />\ndream maker, life taker<br />\nopen up my mind</blockquote><br />\nbut all that I know is it just smoke and mirrors<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdefd9a44cc84de075f73ad20cc63c0b1880a9e3","tid":111973,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hi Brett<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7170e21b85fa6ea94564991aa1d09eee6aaf445","tid":111973,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Demons<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好正<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">don't wanna let you down but I'm hell bound <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"fa853d06ede4ca7062c83d15929caad0aef0b3a1","tid":111973,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Hi Brett<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHi柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFreak"},{"pid":"482228512a9b4434d750d96a75554d5a4a9700ec","tid":111973,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T22:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Hi Brett<im